{"tid":483676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年逾5.7萬人持單程證來港  平均每日157人來港","createTime":"2017-11-29T10:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T00:04:05.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f39fee0297bc1d7012de8fd3f736deb1bb0019b5","tid":483676,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局書面回覆立法會議員質詢時透露，去年有五萬七千多人持單程證來港，是十年新高。<br />\n<br />\n過去十年，共有44.5萬人透過每日150個配額申請單程證來港，每年大約三萬至五萬人。去年的數字是歷年新高，有5.7萬人，平均每日157人來港，比每日150個配額高。按年齡組別區分，佔最多是25至34歲的女性。<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，單程證是內地有關機關製發的證件，受理、審批及簽發屬於內地當局的職權範圍。政府認為，無需要及理據要求內地當局改變現行單程證制度及審批工作。"},{"pid":"c823021deee00eb23a9a34ee4121a8f4fcd01d5c","tid":483676,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"人口清洗<br />\n香港省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba126cdb3eb57bdc276e62bd19331053b39ca27f","tid":483676,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔用365日計仲唔止添呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b92a11ad17d8fe081e636ff8ecf3b7ac63494288","tid":483676,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"佔最多是25至34歲的女性。<br />\n應該有唔少係連登仔老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee859b6b7daabc04f1f7e3e32614c1bd3a8a42d","tid":483676,"uid":39550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"建制話無問題！就用佢一家大細連所有遠近親戚換一張已批嘅證！"},{"pid":"84f7200697c8018c4332ea00c3b1f48d443397ab","tid":483676,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔用365日計仲唔止添呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class